1. 检查是否配置了全局
$ git config -l

2. 配置邮箱
$ git config --global user.name "cloud"
$ git config --global user.email "service@uyger.com"

3. 生成id_rsa和id_rsa.pub
$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "service@uyger.com" -f ~/.ssh/rsa/github
$ vim ~/.ssh/config
$ chmod 600 ~/.ssh/config
<------------------
Host github
    HostName github.com
    User git
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/rsa/github
------------------->

4. 拉取代码
$ git clone git@github:doc.git ./

